context:
KR:
<i>&lt;color=#5bffde&gt;원컨대 내 어깨 밑에 날개라도 돋아</i>&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
<i>&lt;color=#5bffde&gt;Let flourish from my back the pinions of flight,</i>&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
<i>&lt;color=#5bffde&gt;가는 꽃 따라 하늘 높이 날고 지고</i>&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
<i>&lt;color=#5bffde&gt;To chase the parting blossoms, their wilting voyage a sky-high plight.</i>&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
<i>&lt;color=#5bffde&gt;아아, 하늘 끝 어디에 꽃무덤 있을까?</i>&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
<i>&lt;color=#5bffde&gt;Ah, where at the edge of heaven does it lie, this flower-mound?</i>&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
<i>&lt;color=#5bffde&gt;너는 지금 죽어 내가 묻어주지만</i>&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
<i>&lt;color=#5bffde&gt;I bury you today, for you have passed on</i>&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
<i>&lt;color=#5bffde&gt;내가 죽으면 어느 날에 묻힐까?</i>&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
<i>&lt;color=#5bffde&gt;But when will I be buried when I am gone?</i>&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
<i>&lt;color=#5bffde&gt;사람들은 꽃잎 묻어주는 나를 비웃지만</i>&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
<i>&lt;color=#5bffde&gt;I bury the petals, under people’s mocking laughter</i>&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
<i>&lt;color=#5bffde&gt;이다음에 나를 묻어줄 사람은 누구일까?</i>&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
<i>&lt;color=#5bffde&gt;But who shall be burying me then, in the thereafter?</i>&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
<i>&lt;color=#5bffde&gt;묻힌 나를 보고 슬퍼할 이는 없겠지.</i>&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
<i>&lt;color=#5bffde&gt;No one will cry at my burial-mound.</i>&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
<i>&lt;color=#5bffde&gt;어느 날 아침 봄이 다하고 꽃잎 지는 무렵이 오는 것처럼</i>&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
<i>&lt;color=#5bffde&gt;For, as morning springs die and blossoms wilt</i>&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
<i>&lt;color=#5bffde&gt;모든 건 한 무더기 흙으로 흘러가 버리면 그만일 테니.</i>&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
<i>&lt;color=#5bffde&gt;They all float away and turn to silt.</i>&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;안 그래도 찾고 있었어.&gt;
EN:
&lt;Hi, we've been looking for you.&gt;

KR:
&lt;얘들아… 근데 여기…&gt;
EN:
&lt;Guys... uh... &gt;

KR:
&lt;시춘이가 없는데…&gt;
EN:
&lt;Xichun's not here... &gt;
